ED_Title: Provisional programme  of work and timetable of the First Committee for 2023
ED_DecisionText: At its 46th plenary meeting, on 7 December 2022, the General Assembly, on the recommendation of the First Committee, (Footnote: A/77/395, para. 5.) approved the provisional programme of work and timetable of the Committee for 2023, as set out in the annex to the report of the Committee. (Footnote: A/77/395.).
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the main part of the session will be contained in document A/77/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
